high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wall then turn left.
Pick up the wine glass that's in front of you to the right of the stove.
Turn left and take two steps then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Chill the wine glass in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and take a step then turn right to face the coffee maker.
Put the wine glass to the left of the salt on the edge of the table.

high_descs: Walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the wine glass from the counter behind the salt shaker.
Walk to the fridge on the other side of the room.
Put the wine glass in the fridge on the third shelf, close the door, open the door, pick up the wine glass, close the door.
Turn and walk to the white table on the right.
Put the wine glass down on the table to the left of the potato.
anns.task_desc: To chill a wine glass and put it on the table.

Pick up the glass on the counter, right of the stove.
Turn around, bring the glass to the fridge.
Chill the glass in the fridge.

Put the chilled glass on the table, left of the potato.
